19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
21 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 187A-2.1 of Title 73, unless
22 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
23 A. In addition to any other authorization provided by law, the
24 Oklahoma Capitol Improvement Authority is authorized to utilize
